DESCRIPTION:Join us for a virtual interview with Percival Everett\, the 202
 5 Pulitzer Prize winner and one of the most inventive\, fearless voices in
  contemporary fiction. Explore his genre-defying novels\, his creative pro
 cess\, and the stories behind his most celebrated books. Register hereThi
 s event is made possible by Illinois Libraries Present\, a statewide colla
 boration between public libraries offering high-quality events.
