 ails free books to children in participating areas. The program is open to
  children from birth to age five who live in eligible ZIP codes. Books are
  available in both English and Spanish. Children in eligible zip codes can
  register for the program and pick up a free book at the event.Eligible ZI
 P codes for Niles Township:Lincolnwood: 60712Golf: 60029Morton Grove: 6005
 3Niles: 60714Skokie: 60073\, 60077\, 60203Can't make our event? Head to on
 e of the other Niles Township kick-off events listed below:Skokie Public L
 ibrary\, Saturday\, April 25\, 9:30am\, skokielibrary.infoNiles Maine Dist
 rict Library\, Monday\, April 27\, 7pm\, nileslibrary.orgEarly Childhood A
 lliance Fun Fair\, Saturday\, May 2\, 10am-1pm\, nilestownshipeca.orgLinco
 lnwood Public Library\, Sunday\, May 9\, 10:30am\, lincolnwoodlibrary.org
CATEGORIES:Books & Authors
